N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4030.4 - In a walkover

State Regulations
(a) In case
of a walkover, one half of the money offered to the winner is given. (b) When a walkover is the result of
arrangement by owners of horses engaged, no portion of the added money nor any
other prize need be given. Notes
